{"title":"2024 Orbea Rallon Enduro Bike Gets Faster, Longer, Slacker Upgrade","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2024-orbea-rallon-omr-carbon-enduro-mountain-bike/","date":1697559444000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB_updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, EDR Chatel racing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_UCI-EDR-World-Cup-Chatel-racing-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Another full overhaul to Orbea’s enduro Rallon means a faster, shreddier (<em>more shreddy?</em>) mountain bike built to go faster on the toughest tracks. Just like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-orbea-rallon-enduro-mountain-bike-linkage-adds-travel-and-its-backwards-compatible/\" target=\"_blank\">new 2019 link</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-orbea-rallon-gets-mullet-option-heaps-of-frame-storage-and-new-geometry/\" target=\"_blank\">2022 mullet option</a> of its previous generations over the past four years, this new Rallon again bumps up to longer travel and even slacker geometry to “Focus on Fast”. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2024 Orbea Rallon OMR Carbon enduro mountain bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike.jpg\" alt=\"Orbea Rallon OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all photos c. Orbea</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you’re racing the UCI EDR enduro Word Cup or turning laps at your local bikepark, the new Orbea Rallon is up for “<em>hitting the biggest gaps in the park, smashing berms, and scorning braking bumps. Forget limits, forget distractions, just focus on fast.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A lot has changed. But a lot has still stayed the same. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Orbea Rallon looks a lot like the previous generation that first debuted a surprising 6 years ago. Sure, there was a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-orbea-rallon-enduro-mountain-bike-linkage-adds-travel-and-its-backwards-compatible/\" target=\"_blank\">new link</a> that made that bike more capable in 2019. Then, another a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-orbea-rallon-gets-mullet-option-heaps-of-frame-storage-and-new-geometry/\" target=\"_blank\">mullet option</a> introduced in 2022 that also brought internal frame storage and further refined linkages. But this new enduro bike will look and feel familiar to long-time Rallon fans.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>So, What’s New?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop.jpg\" alt=\"Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, UCI EDR Chatel rock drop\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-UCI-EDR-Chatel-drop-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But what’s really new is more travel and more capable geometry. The 2024 Orbea Rallon keeps the same 170mm fork travel up front. But now it gets an upgrade to 167mm in the rear to soak up bigger hits. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, large geometry updates\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_updated-geo-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Rallon also slackens it’s headtube just 1/2° from last year, a subtle refinement they realized mid race season. With the adjustable geometry, that means you can now pick from a 63.5°/64° angle up front.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, geometry table\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_geometry-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Other than head angle, frame geometry is unchanged. The new bike keeps the same Stack, Reach, chainstay length, BB height &amp; standover as in <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2022-orbea-rallon-gets-mullet-option-heaps-of-frame-storage-and-new-geometry/\" target=\"_blank\">last year’s</a> update. Pick from <em>Low</em> or <em>Lower</em> with the carry-over flip-chip at the lower shock mount.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What else stays the same?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, X-Ray frameset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_X-ray-frameset-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new asymmetric Rallon is still built from Orbea’s next-to-top-tier OMR carbon for a mix of lightweight, stiffness, and durability. And the bike can still be built up with either 29″ wheels front &amp; rear. Or build a mullet with a 27.5″ rear wheel and the included shock extender. You also still get the Lockr internal frame storage inside the downtube, under the water bottle mount.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, angled detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Orbea calls the 4 sizes with lots of standover clearance “Steep &amp; Deep” so riders can often fit on more than one size. Then, pick your preferred bike based on your riding style, and Reach &amp; wheelbase preference.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2024 Orbea Rallon – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, in forest green\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_forest-green-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, in mars red\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_mars-red-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 2024 Orbea Rallon OMR Carbon enduro bike come in 4 sizes (S-XL). It gets 2 colors – Forest green or Mars red. And there are 5 stock builds. It’s also possible to get a custom finish in the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/orbeas-updated-myo-custom-program-gives-you-1-4-million-combos-to-have-it-your-way/\" target=\"_blank\">MyO</a> customizer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, M20\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M20_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Orbea Rallon M20</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The most “affordable” build starts at $5399 / 5000€ for the 2024 Orbea Rallon M20 with Fox 38 &amp; Float X Performance suspension, a Shimano SLX groupset &amp; 30mm internal RaceFace AR alloy wheels. At $6600 / 6000€, the M10 build keeps the same suspension. But it upgrades to XT and Orbea’s house brand Oquo MC32Team alloy wheels. The Orbea Rallon M11 AXS at $7000 / 6500€ then upgrades that with a SRAM GX Eagle AXS wireless electronic groupset and Code Bronze brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting a real performance upgrade, the Rallon M-Team that goes all-in with a Fox 38 Factory fork, X2 Factory shock, Transfer Factory dropper, complete Shimano XT group, Oquo carbon cockpit, and those alloy Oquo MC32Team wheels. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, M-LTD\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-M-LTD_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Orbea Rallon M-LTD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Topping out the carbon enduro bike builds is 2024 Orbea Rallon M-LTD. It gets Factory Fox 38 fork, DHX2 shock &amp; Transfer dropper, plus a T-Type SRAM XX Eagle AXS transmission and carbon Oquo MC32LTD wheels.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Any of the other bikes can also be up-spec’d with those carbon wheels, carbon cockpit, DHX2 shock, or even DH casing tires, if you want. All the stock complete bike builds are 29er only. But you can customize in the MyO customizer to get a mullet setup direct from Orbea.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Orbea Rallon MTB, updated OMR carbon enduro race mountain bike, racing Loudenvielle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2024-Orbea-Rallon-MTB_updated-OMR-carbon-enduro-race-mountain-bike_2023-EDR-WC-Loudenvielle-mountains-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Rallon is technically a MY24 bike. So, reach out to your local Orbea dealer to see how quickly they can get you on one in time for riding next season.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.orbea.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Orbea.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2024-orbea-rallon-omr-carbon-enduro-mountain-bike/\">2024 Orbea Rallon Enduro Bike Gets Faster, Longer, Slacker Upgrade</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"845fcb9efdb41760193c950ef943078dc5ca050a74661d8a44ab1f749aa5fe79","category":"Cycling"}